Package: niarules
Type: Package
Title: Numerical Association Rule Mining Using Nature-Inspired Algorithms in R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Iztok Fister, Jr. <iztok@iztok.space> [orcid:https://orcid.org/0000-0002-6418-1272]
Maintainer: Iztok Fister, Jr. <iztok@iztok.space>
Classification/ACM: G.4, H.2.8
Description: This package is an R framework designed for mining numerical association rules through the utilization of nature-inspired algorithms for optimization. Drawing inspiration from both the NiaARM Python package and NiaARM.jl package, this repository introduces the capability to perform numerical association rule mining in the R programming language.
URL: https://github.com/firefly-cpp/niarules
BugReports: https://github.com/firefly-cpp/niarules/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
Imports:
    stats,
    utils
Suggests:
  testthat
